title: SodaStream Power: The Power Is In Your Hands
description: Introducing Power, the new automatic Sparkling Water Maker from SodaStream.

asset.author: SodaStream
asset.hookText: Introducing Power, the new automatic Sparkling Water Maker from SodaStream.

transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING] Power. The possession of control. The ability to make things happen. 

[MUSIC PLAYING] 

Precise down to the last detail. 

[MUSIC PLAYING] 

You now have the power to turn plain water into fresh sparkling water creations in seconds with a touch of a button. 

[MUSIC PLAYING] 

Effortless, convenient, and perfectly precise, so you can make it just the way you like. The new Sodastream Power automatic sparkling water maker. The power is in your hands. 

[MUSIC PLAYING]
